  '<ul>',
  '<li><strong>Magic-byte missing</strong> — buffer doesn\'t start with <code>%PDF-</code>.</li>',
  '<li><strong>JavaScript action (`/JS` / `/JavaScript`)</strong> — RCE class in vulnerable readers (Adobe / Foxit / nitro CVEs). Universally refused.</li>',
